snippet.title: Aaryan - Tamil Teaser | Vishnu Vishal | Praveen K | Ghibran | Selvaraghavan | Shraddha S | 31st Oct
snippet.description:
Presenting the official Tamil teaser of Aaryan starring Vishnu Vishal. The film comes to theatres worldwide on the 31st of October 2025. 

A film by Praveen K
Produced by Vishnu Vishal Studioz

DOP - Harish Kannan
Music - Ghibran 
Editor - San Lokesh
Stunts - Stunt Silva, PC Stunts Prabhu
Additional Screenplay - Manu Anand
Production Design - S. Jayachandran
Costume Designer and Stylist - Vinod Sundar 
Additional styling - Varshini Sankar
Sound Design - Sachin Sudhakaran, Hariharan N (Sync Cinema)

snippet.title: Mango Pachcha Teaser | Sanchii | Viveka | KRG Studios | Supriyanvi Studio | CharanRaj | KRG Connects
snippet.description:
The upcoming collaborative biggie of KRG Studios and Supriyanvi Picture Studio #Sanchii01 has revealed its title through a promo of the lead actor Sanchii on account of his birthday. This promo unveils the character of the lead actor and the title of the film. 

"MANGO PACHCHA" is a film that tells the story of an unapologetically ambitious and adventurous man in the city of Mysuru. Based on various real events between the 90‚Äôs and 2010, this film will offer great characters, intense drama and unique storyline. It will be a quintessential ode to the city of Mysore through a maverick character. 

The film stars Sanchii aka Junior Kichcha, Malashree, Mayur Patel, Kajal Kunder and others, it's directed by Viveka. The film is produced by Karthik and Yogi G Raj under the banner of KRG Studios in collaboration with Priya Sudeep under the banner of Supriyanvi Picture Studio. The Action-Cut begins from February 10th.

MOVIE CREDITS
Producers: Priya Sudeep, Karthik & Yogi G Raj
Director: Viveka
Written by: Viveka, Nagbhushan Deshpande
Cast: Sanchith Sanjeev, Kajal Kunder, Prashanth Hiremath, Mayur Patel, Jai Gopinath, Harini Srikanth, Hamsa, Ugramm Manju

The upcoming collaborative biggie of KRG Studios and Supriyanvi Picture Studio #Sanchii01 has revealed its title through a promo of the lead actor Sanchii on account of his birthday. This promo unveils the character of the lead actor and the title of the film. 

"MANGO PACHCHA" is a film that tells the story of an unapologetically ambitious and adventurous man in the city of Mysuru. Based on various real events between the 90‚Äôs and 2010, this film will offer great characters, intense drama and unique storyline. It will be a quintessential ode to the city of Mysore through a maverick character. 

The film stars Sanchii aka Junior Kichcha, Malashree, Mayur Patel, Kajal Kunder and others, it's directed by Viveka. The film is produced by Karthik and Yogi G Raj under the banner of KRG Studios in collaboration with Priya Sudeep under the banner of Supriyanvi Picture Studio. The Action-Cut begins from February 10th.
